OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMostly
OL,6,Fcloudy during Monday evening, with
OL,7,Fthis low enough to produce hill fog
OL,8,Fover the mountains and the odd spot of
OL,9,Fdrizzle. A few clearer spells emerging
OL,10,Finto the early hours of Tuesday. A
OL,11,Fwarm and rather muggy night.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FA grey and murky start as low
OL,14,Fcloud lifts. Outbreaks of rain
OL,15,Farriving through the day, turning
OL,16,Fheavy over the hills. Hill and coastal
OL,17,Ffog returning by evening. Feeling
OL,18,Fhumid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
