OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FUnsettled at times over the coming
OL,7,Fdays with showers and spells of rain.
OL,8,FHowever, some drier, warmer and
OL,9,Fbrighter interludes are possible too.
OL,10,FRemaining humid.
